summary: An email from an FBI Special Agent to a recipient (M) inquiring if they have time for a call with an Assistant United States Attorney (AUSA) regarding Ghislaine Maxwell. The document indicates ongoing coordination between law enforcement and prosecutors in the Maxwell case in April 2021.

events.title: Email Request for Call Regarding Maxwell
events.description: An FBI Special Agent emails M to inquire about scheduling a call with an Assistant United States Attorney (AUSA) to discuss Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: An FBI Special Agent from the New York Field Office was coordinating a call regarding Ghislaine Maxwell in late April 2021.
The communication involves an Assistant United States Attorney (AUSA), indicating prosecutorial activity in the Maxwell case at that time.
The recipient (M) was possibly at training, suggesting they may be a law enforcement officer or agent involved in the investigation.
